    • Method Detail

      • matches

        @RunsInCurrentThread
public boolean matches(@Nullable
                                  Component c)

        Indicates whether the type and visibility of the given AWT or Swing Component matches the value specified in this matcher.

        Note: This method is accessed in the current executing thread. Such thread may or may not be the event dispatch thread (EDT.) Client code must call this method from the EDT.

        Parameters:
        c - the Component to verify.
        Returns:
        true if the type and visibility of the given Component matches the values specified in this matcher, false otherwise.
